data.description: Welcome to your exceptional front brick, 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath home on a full, finished walk-out basement that includes a guest suite. Formal dining and study on the main level accompanied by updated kitchen and spacious family room. Additionally, you will find upgraded flooring throughout the home and exquisite details to the design of each room. The fenced backyard yields privacy for family entertainment or furry little friends that need a safe space to enjoy the outdoors. This home is PRICED TO SELL and eagerly waiting its new family. This beautiful home in the highly desired Brookwood High School district will not last long.
